- bin/create-project.ts
- src/index.ts

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] `bun run bin/create-project.ts` executes
- [ ] All steps called in correct order
- [ ] Errors handled gracefully
- [ ] Exit codes correct (0=success, 1=error)

