## Task
Implement template copying logic that recursively copies template directories.

## API Design
```typescript
interface CopyOptions {
  // Variables for replacement
  variables: TemplateVariables;
  // Files/dirs to skip
  exclude?: string[];
  // Only copy these (if specified)
  include?: string[];
  // Transform file names (remove .template extension)
  transformFileName?: (name: string) => string;
}

async function copyTemplate(
  templateDir: string,
  destDir: string,
  options: CopyOptions
): Promise<string[]>; // Returns list of created files
```

## Implementation Notes
- Recursively walk template directory
- Apply variable replacement to file contents
- Remove .template extension from file names
- Skip files not relevant to selected modules
- Return list of files for dry-run display

